{
  "stem": "17761.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He's a sentimental person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he used to compose songs there, and we used to sing it together and to dream about [HEBREW] Israel, something is a dream that we-- it was so dark around that only a little bit of light we could find in our heart, and nowhere outside.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this was a very important activity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It kept us together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we used to also to communicate to each other when there were dangerous situations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Or something that we knew that was important to be communicated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a kind of-- verbally, no telephone, [LAUGHS] nothing else, and not in a written way, anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we used from mouth to mouth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- by the way, in the ghetto, there was a lot of such information going through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One heard from an officer in the German army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One heard an officer from the Romanian army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We even had two [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We called it [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "YPA, ?] which means [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That means the agency for Jewish gossip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the other was called [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "YVA-- ?] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]-- Jews Walk Like This.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's a part of the folklore that has been there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this-- often or not, there were presentations-- theater presentations-- by the children, to which this-- to which we invited the authorities-- the Romanian authorities and the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to come there, even these two infamous persons that everybody-- every Jew who lived in Mogilev remembers them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the two-- two from the Romanian army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One called Barbelescu-- B-A-R-B-U-L-E-S-C-U, who was then tried and-- and sentenced, not to death, but a-- as a war criminal.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
